sources.description:
Connor Ryan, broke and single, returns to Atlantic City to rebuild his life with the last source of income that he has: a few condos that sit in the shadows of the city's casinos.   Unfortunately, Connor's tenants don't want to pay him.  Facing the kind of real estate troubles that will make your home-hunting problems seem like a walk in the park, Connor turns to extreme means in order to collect from his deadbeat tenants.

Directed by Michael Clayton
2017
Starring        James Caprinello, Dawn-Lyen Gardner
